  <title>Applying user interface customizations at startup</title>
  <purpose>It is unsafe to make user interface customizations before the ArcGIS application framework has fully initialized. This sample shows you how to use IApplicationStatusEvents and IApplicationStatus inside a custom extension to monitor the framework's state and properly apply interface customizations when the extension loads.</purpose>
